      "timestampEdited": null,
      "callEndedTimestamp": null,
      "isPinned": false,
      "content": "Yes, I'll try overriding the Yosys version with 0.63 in the project template for now.\nI think LibreLane should be able to create a standalone reproducible, as it does for OpenROAD. Maybe pyosys complicates things, but we'll see.\nThe easiest way would be to write a small Yosys script that reads the Verilog and reproduces the issue, but I'm not sure it will be that easy :)",
