      "timestampEdited": null,
      "callEndedTimestamp": null,
      "isPinned": false,
      "content": "If this runs through I can properly rebase everything and finally update nix-eda in LibreLane again.\n\nhttps://github.com/librelane/librelane/pull/916/changes/d867039ca70d301a784f5b65e206076372d635b0",
